"Based on the retrieved posts, the \"putinmissing\" event involves conflicting narratives between official briefings and unverified social media claims.\n\n**Verified Information:**\n*   Official accounts cite three distinct internal developments: a private police bulletin (linked to 73 cases), a hidden evacuation order (linked to 7 cases), and a second sealed scene (linked to 23 cases).\n\n**Disputed/Unverified Claims:**\n*   Unverified users claim visual evidence of Putin's presence (\"There he is!!\") and allege missing elements from the top of the Kremlin, using hashtags like #putindead.\n\n**Conclusion:**\nThe core dispute lies between official records detailing sealed scenes and evacuation orders versus unverified assertions of Putin's visibility and physical absence from the Kremlin."